://www.vox.com/culture/2020/3/26/21193180/unorthodox-netflix-streaming-series-review|dead-url=no}}</ref><ref>{{Cite web|url=https://www.newyorker.com/culture/on-television/unorthodox-reviewed-a-young-womans-remarkable-flight-from-hasidic-williamsburg|title="Unorthodox," Reviewed: A Young Woman’s Remarkable Flight from Hasidic Williamsburg|last=Syme|first=Rachel|date=2020-04-09|website=[[The_New_Yorker|The New Yorker]]|language=en|access-date=2020-04-13|quote=Haas’s remarkable performance manages to convey the reserves of pain, both personal and communal, in Esty’s story.|archive-date=2021-01-22|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20210122131154/https://www.newyorker.com/culture/on-television/unorthodox-reviewed-a-young-womans-remarkable-flight-from-hasidic-williamsburg|dead-url=no}}</ref><ref>{{Cite web|url=https://www.bostonglobe.com/2020/04/15/arts/theres-mesmerizing-moving-performance-heart-unorthodox/|title=There’s a mesmerizing and moving performance at the heart of ‘Unorthodox’|last=Gilbert|first=Matthew|date=2020-04-15|website=[[Boston_Globe|Boston Globe]]|language=en-US|access-date=2020-04-15|archive-date=2020-12-07|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20201207131823/https://www.bostonglobe.com/2020/04/15/arts/theres-mesmerizing-moving-performance-heart-unorthodox/|dead-url=no}}</ref><ref>{{Cite web|url=https://www.goldderby.com/article/2020/unorthodox-shira-haas-netflix-emmys/|title=‘Unorthodox’: Here’s the unlikely uplifting heroine you need to root for right now|last=Wloszczyna|first=Susan|date=2020-04-02|website=[[Gold_Derby|Gold Derby]]|language=en-US|access-date=2020-04-15|quote=Haas by all rights deserves to be treated as a full-blown star|archive-date=2020-12-06|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20201206075916/https://www.goldderby.com/article/2020/unorthodox-shira-haas-netflix-emmys/|dead-url=no}}</ref><ref name=":1">{{Cite web|url=https://variety.com/2020/tv/features/unorthdox-shira-haas-yiddish-hassidic-judaism-contemporary-german-culture-netflix-audiences-1203543816/|title=‘Unorthodox’ Star Shira Haas Brings Yiddish, Hassidic Judaism and Contemporary German Culture to Netflix|last=Saval|first=Malina|date=2020-03-26|website=[[Variety_(magazine)|Variety]]|language=en|access-date=2020-04-13|archive-date=2020-03-28|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20200328024853/https://variety.com/2020/tv/features/unorthdox-shira-haas-yiddish-hassidic-judaism-contemporary-german-culture-netflix-audiences-1203543816/|dead-url=no}}</ref>。凭借《离经叛道》，哈斯获得了[[第72届黄金时段艾美奖|黄金时段艾美奖]]最佳有限劇集或電視電影女主角的提名<ref name=emmy>{{cite web |title=2020 Primetime Emmy® Awards – Nomination Press Release |url=https://www.emmys.com/sites/default/files/Downloads/72nd-nominations-list-v1.pdf?q=1 |publisher=[[Academy_of_Television_Arts_&_Sciences|Academy of Television Arts & Sciences]] |accessdate=2020-07-28 |archive-date=2020-07-28 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20200728162008/https://www.emmys.com/sites/default/files/Downloads/72nd-nominations-list-v1.pdf?q=1 |dead-url=yes }}</ref>。

== 早年生活 ==
希拉·哈斯1995年5月11日<ref>{{Cite web|url=http://www.allocine.fr/personne/fichepersonne_gen_cpersonne=716558.html|title=Shira Haas|last=AlloCine|website=[[AlloCiné|AlloCiné]]|language=fr|dead-url=no|access-date=2020-04-14|archive-date=2020-12-06|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20201206131927/https://www.allocine.fr/personne/fichepersonne_gen_cpersonne=716558.html}}</ref>出生于以色列[[特拉维夫|特拉维夫]]的一个[[犹太|犹太]]家庭<ref name=":2">{{Cite web|url=http://lists.forbes.co.il/2019under30/שירה-האס/|title=Forbes Israel 30 Under 30: שירה האס|date=2019-01-17|website=[[Forbes|Forbes]]|language=he-IL|dead-url=no|access-date=2020-04-14|archive-date=2020-02-08|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20200208022859/http://lists.forbes.co.il/2019under30/%D7%A9%D7%99%D7%A8%D7%94-%D7%94%D7%90%D7%A1/}}</ref><ref name=":4">{{Cite web|url=https://www.maariv.co.il/culture/movies/Article-693206|title=שירה האס: "הבראתי לפני 20 שנה, אך אין ספק שהסרטן הוא חלק ממני"|last=Levin|first=Talia|date=2019-04-07|website=[[Maariv|Maariv]]|trans-title=Shira Haas: 'I gave it up 20 years ago, but the cancer is definitely still a part of me'|access-date=2020-04-15|archive-date=2019-04-07|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20190407194714/https://www.maariv.co.il/culture/movies/Article-693206|dead-url=no}}</ref>。她的父母都是萨布拉人，有[[波兰犹太人历史|波兰]]、匈牙利和捷克血统。她的祖父是一名大屠杀幸存者，二战期间被关押在[[奥斯威辛集中营|奥斯威辛集中营]]中<ref name=":3">{{Cite web|url=http://www.mtv.com/news/3161057/shira-haas-unorthodox-interview/|title='Unorthodox' Remembers Atrocities Of The Past While Stepping Bravely Into The Future|last=Tilchen|first=Jordyn|date=2020-03-26|website=[[MTV_News|MTV News]]|dead-url=no|access-date=2020-04-15|archive-date=2020-12-08|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20201208173446/https://www.mtv.com/news/3161057/shira-haas-unorthodox-interview/}}</ref>。一岁时，她随父母搬到[[霍德夏沙隆|霍德夏沙隆]]<ref name=":4" />，在这度过了她儿时的大部分时间<ref>{{Cite web|url=https://www.ynet.co.il/entertainment/article/rJE977IBI|title=שירה האס: 'לא אוכל לגלם צעירות לנצח, אני כבר מרגישה את זה'|last=Bogen|first=Amir|date=2020-03-14|website=[[Ynet|Ynet]]|language=en|trans-title=Shira Haas: "I can't play young women forever, I already feel it"|dead-url=no|access-date=2020-04-15|archive-date=2020-12-06|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20201206074107/https://www.ynet.co.il/entertainment/article/rJE977IBI}}</ref>。两岁时，哈斯曾被诊断出患有肾癌，经过一系列严厉的治疗，两年后获得康复<ref name=":0">{{Cite web|url=https://www.yediot.co.il/articles/0,7340,L-5382464,00.html|title="ככל שהזמן עובר, אודישנים, תפקידים ואולי גם החיים, נהיים עבורי יותר קלים"|last=Segal|first=Itai|date=2018-10-31|website=[[Yedioth_Ahronoth|Yedioth Ahronoth]]|language=he|trans-title=As time goes on, auditions, roles and even life get better for me|dead-url=no|access-date=2020-04-15|archive-date=2021-01-05|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20210105123230/https://www.yediot.co.il/articles/0,7340,L-5382464,00.html}}</ref>。

== 演艺事业 ==
在出演《离经叛道》之前，哈斯因出演以色列剧情电影和电视中的角色而获得全国性的知名度。

在获得出演《[[离经叛道|离经叛道]]》的机会后，哈斯在剧集拍摄前两个月抵达柏林，以便学习该剧中主要使用的[[意第绪语|意第绪语]]<ref>{{Cite web|url=https://www.indiewire.com/2020/04/unorthodox-netflix-shira-haas-interview-1202222687/|title=‘Unorthodox’: How Shira Haas Crafted Her Riveting Performance in the Netflix Drama|last=Dry|first=Jude|date=2020-04-04|website=[[IndieWire|IndieWire]]|language=en|access-date=2020-04-16|archive-date=2020-04-07|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20200407061354/https://www.indiewire.com/2020/04/unorthodox-netflix-shira-haas-interview-1202222687/|dead-url=no}}</ref>。除了意第绪语课程，哈斯还被要求剃光头，同时完成了钢琴和歌唱课程，以便为扮演住在[[纽约|纽约]][[威廉斯堡_(布魯克林)|布鲁克林区威廉斯堡]]的Esther "Esty" Shapiro一角做准备，她逃离了自己的包办婚姻和[[哈雷迪犹太教|极端正统犹太教]]<ref>{{Cite web|title=Shira Haas Describes Overnight Fame And How Netflix’s ‘Unorthodox’ Is A Universally Groundbreaking Story Of Escape|url=https://www.vogue.co.uk/arts-and-lifestyle/article/shira-haas-netflix-unorthodox-interview|last=Seth|first=Radhika|date=2020-04-27|website=[[British_Vogue|British Vogue]]|language=en-GB|access-date=2020-05-02|archive-date=2020-05-06|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20200506085022/https://www.vogue.co.uk/arts-and-lifestyle/article/shira-haas-netflix-unorthodox-interview|dead-url=no}}</ref><ref>{{Cite web|url=https://www.elle.com/uk/life-and-culture/culture/a32155188/unorthodox-netflix/|title=Unorthodox: The True Story Behind The Hit Netflix Show|last=O'Malley|first=Katie|date=2020-04-15|website=ELLE|language=en-GB|access-date=2020-04-16|archive-date=2020-04-17|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20200417040706/https://www.elle.com/uk/life-and-culture/culture/a32155188/unorthodox-netflix/|dead-url=no}}</ref>。该剧由Netflix根据{{le|德博拉·费尔德曼|Deborah Feldman}}真实生活故事自传《{{le|离经叛道：丑态百出的拒绝我的哈西迪根源|Unorthodox: The Scandalous Rejection of My Hasidic Roots|离-{经叛}-道：丑态百出的拒绝我的哈西迪根源}}》改编<ref>{{Cite web|url=https://www.indiewire.com/2020/04/unorthodox-netflix-shira-haas-interview-1202222687/|title=‘Unorthodox’: How Shira Haas Crafted Her Riveting Performance in the Netflix Drama|last=Dry|first=Jude|last2=Dry|first2=Jude|date=2020-04-04|website=IndieWire|language=en|access-date=2020-04-26|archive-date=2020-04-07|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20200407061354/https://www.indiewire.com/2020/04/unorthodox-netflix-shira-haas-interview-1202222687/|dead-url=no}}</ref>。剧集播出之后，影评人对哈斯的表演给出了极高的评价。《[[纽约时报|纽约时报]]》的詹姆斯·波尼沃兹克将哈斯描述为"现象级，富有表现力和迷人。"<ref>{{Cite news|last=Poniewozik|first=James|url=https://www.nytimes.com/2020/03/25/arts/television/unorthodox-review-netflix.html|title=Review: ‘Unorthodox,’ a Stunning Escape From Brooklyn|date=2020-03-25|work=The New York Times|access-date=2020-04-16|language=en-US|issn=0362-4331|archive-date=2020-03-25|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20200325190005/https://www.nytimes.com/2020/03/25/arts/television/unorthodox-review-netflix.html|dead-url=no}}</ref> 《[[卫报|卫报]]》的布里吉德·德莱尼将她描述为 "令人着迷"和"杰出"，并指出"身体娇小，就像一个孩子，观众会立即对她产生保护。"<ref>{{Cite news|last=Delaney|first=Brigid|url=https://www.theguardian.com/culture/2020/apr/20/unorthodox-a-thrilling-story-of-rebellion-and-freedom-from-new-york-to-berlin|title=Unorthodox: a thrilling story of rebellion and freedom from New York to Berlin|date=2020-04-19|work=[[The_Guardian|The Guardian]]|access-date=2020-04-19|dead-url=no|language=en-GB|issn=0261-3077|archive-date=2020-04-19|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20200419174908/https://www.theguardian.com/culture/2020/apr/20/unorthodox-a-thrilling-story-of-rebellion-and-freedom-from-new-york-to-berlin}}</ref>《[[福布斯|福布斯]]》的希娜·斯科特写道，哈斯"提供了一个令人难以置信的表演，饰演Esty，充满了微妙，巧妙地揭示了她的角色内心的挣扎和幸福，不需要说一个字。"<ref>{{Cite web|url=https://www.forbes.com/sites/sheenascott/2020/03/31/unorthodox-review-portrait-of-a-young-woman-finding-freedom-in-berlin/|title=‘Unorthodox’ Review: Portrait Of A Young Woman Finding Freedom In Berlin|last=Scott|first=Sheena|date=2020-03-31|website=Forbes|language=en|access-date=2020-04-16|archive-date=2020-04-01|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20200401212607/https://www.forbes.com/sites/sheenascott/2020/03/31/unorthodox-review-portrait-of-a-young-woman-finding-freedom-in-berlin/|dead-url=no}}</ref>《[[华盛顿邮报|华盛顿邮报]]》的汉克·斯图弗写道，她"为这个角色赋予了一种严肃而又脆弱的光彩。"<ref>{{Cite web|url=https://www.washingtonpost.com/entertainment/tv/unorthodox-carefully-and-beautifully-depicts-a-young-womans-flight-from-tradition/2020/03/25/f36ab420-6d2d-11ea-a3ec-70d7479d83f0_story.html|title=Review {{!}} ‘Unorthodox’ carefully and beautifully depicts a young woman’s flight from tradition|last=Stuever|first=Hank|date=2020-03-25|website=[[Washington_Post|Washington Post]]|language=en|access-date=2020-04-16|archive-date=2020-03-26|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20200326023725/https://www.washingtonpost.com/entertainment/tv/unorthodox-carefully-and-beautifully-depicts-a-young-womans-flight-from-tradition/2020/03/25/f36ab420-6d2d-11ea-a3ec-70d7479d83f0_story.html|dead-url=no}}</ref>

2020年7月28日，哈斯凭借Esty这一角色获得了[[第72届黄金时段艾美奖|黄金时段艾美奖]]最佳有限劇集或電視電影女主角的提名<ref name=emmy />。

